Class ReadWriteSerializable

  • java.lang.Object
    • gateways.ReadWriteSerializable

  • public class ReadWriteSerializable
extends java.lang.Object
    This class will allow (de)serialization of files. Modified to serialize and deserialize data for all 4 data types: Conversations, Events, Rooms, and Events.
